      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[...] Letter to ¶ Baron Dr Friedr. von Mueller, ¶ Director of the botanic and zoological Gardens, ¶ Melbourne ¶ , ¶ Australia....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">71.07.12</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Johann von Wächter</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Bestand E 56 Bü. 28, Hauptstaatsarchiv, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found. The text given here is a much corrected draft. For reply, see M to J. von Wächter, 8 October 1871.</p>
               </note>[...]Schr. an den</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Freihherrn Dr. Friedr. von Müller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Direktor des botan u. zoolog. Gartens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">in <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Melbourne</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Australien</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">d. d. 12 Juli 1871.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Euer Hochwohlgeboren</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>habe ich zu benachrichtigen die Ehre dass S. M. der König dem Antrage entsprechend welchen ich zur Anerkennung der von Ihnen gegen Württemberg, Ihr Geburtsland so vielfach u erfolgreich bethätigten Anhänglichkeit u. Liberalität, insbesonders Ihrer erheblichen Verdienste um die wissenschaftlichen Sammlungen d. Staats Höchstdemselben unterbreitet habe, [...]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible</seg>.</p>
               </note> wollte, Sie in den erblichen Freiherrn Stand des Königsreichs zu erheben.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vermöge höchster Entschliessung v. 6. d. M. haben Seine Maj. diesem [meinem] Antrage auf das Gnädigste zu willfahren geruht, und es gereicht mir zum lebhaften Vergnügen [...] Euer Hochw. zu dieser wohl verdienten Auszeichnung meinen aufrichtigen Glückwunsch auszudrücken.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Behufs der Anfertigung Ihres Freiherrn Diploms möchte ich Sie nun ersuchen mir Ihren vollständigen Namen nebst Titel etc. und eine möglichst deutliche Zeichnung Ihres Wappens wie Sie solches nach der Ihnen zu Theil gewordenen Standeserhöhung zu führen beabsichtigen gef. mittheilen zu wollen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sollten sie in letzter Beziehung besondere Wünsche haben so bin ich gerne bereit denselben Rechnung zu tragen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Empfangen E. H. bei diesem Anlass zugleich die Versicherung meiner ausgezeichneten Hochachtung</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">St.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Stuttgart.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">[...] Letter to</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Dr Friedr. von Mueller,<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">An inter-office memorandum in the same file, dated 21 July 1871, corrected the official record of M’s first name.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Director of the botanic and zoological Gardens,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Melbourne</hi>
               </seg>,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Australia.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">dated 12 July 1871.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to inform you that His Majesty, the King, in accordance with the application I made in recognition of the loyalty and liberality you have so frequently and successfully displayed towards Württemberg, the land of your birth,<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Ministerial error: M was born in Mecklenburg.</p>
               </note> and especially of your considerable services for the State scientific collection, of which I informed His Highness, [...].<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">German text illegible.</p>
               </note> to raise you to the hereditary rank of a Baron of the Kingdom.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>According to the highest decision of the 6th of this month, His Majesty has deigned to graciously grant this my application and it is my great pleasure, Sir, to express to you my sincere congratulations on this well-earned distinction.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In order to facilitate the drawing up of the baronial certificate I must now ask you kindly to communicate to me your complete name with title, etc., and a drawing, as clear as possible, of the coat-of-arms you intend to bear following your rise in rank.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall be pleased to take into account any special wishes you might have concerning the latter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Receive, Sir, on this occasion the assurance of my high esteem<note xml:id="ftn7" type="footnote" n="7">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Draft is unsigned.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Stuttgart.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
